            <div class="space-y-6 text-on-surface-variant font-body-md">
                <p>Founded in 1999, SteelCrest Roofing began with a single mission: to provide the most durable and aesthetically refined roofing solutions for Austin's most prestigious estates and commercial landmarks.</p>
                <p>Our values are rooted in the principles of structural integrity and transparent communication. Every project we undertake is a testament to our philosophy that a roof is not just a protective barrier, but a crowning architectural statement.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-6">
                    <div>
                        <span class="block font-headline-sm text-primary">25+</span>
                        <span class="font-label-caps text-on-secondary-fixed-variant text-sm">Years of Experience</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="block font-headline-sm text-primary">5,000+</span>
                        <span class="font-label-caps text-on-secondary-fixed-variant text-sm">Completed Projects</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 reveal" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
            <div class="relative group">
                <div class="absolute -inset-4 border-2 border-secondary-container/20 translate-x-4 translate-y-4 -z-10 group-hover:translate-x-2 group-hover:translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500 rounded-sm"></div>
